1
00:00:02,780 --> 00:00:04,540
Choi Soo Ji.

2
00:00:06,130 --> 00:00:09,590
Don't use our friendship like this, as a weapon.

3
00:00:12,280 --> 00:00:14,600
If you're like this next time,

4
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:19,790
I'm not sure if I'll be able to hold you back.

5
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:24,360
[Episode 15] 
Your father's seeing another woman!

6
00:00:29,360 --> 00:00:31,870
They seem to have known each other for a long time.

7
00:00:31,870 --> 00:00:36,530
They're similar in age, she's pleasant, and she seems like someone anyone would like...

8
00:00:38,060 --> 00:00:40,300
But, how am I supposed to stop my mom?

9
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:43,610
Where? How did you see it?

10
00:00:43,610 --> 00:00:47,150
- Listen to me. I'm talking about my mom!
- Who is it!?

11
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,670
Tell me.

12
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:54,880
Why should I?

13
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,140
Our friendship, you said?

14
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:04,480
You're the one who shouldn't use our friendship as a weapon.

15
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:48,530
[Vice Chairman Kwon Seok Woo]

16
00:01:48,530 --> 00:01:51,400
I heard what happened. Are you okay?

17
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:53,030
Yes, I am.

18
00:01:53,030 --> 00:01:55,460
There have to be events like this so that we can come out with great momentum.

19
00:01:55,460 --> 00:01:57,830
There weren't any reporters there, right?

20
00:01:57,830 --> 00:02:01,950
Just in case, I instructed the publicity team to prevent it from getting on social media.

21
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:06,290
- You didn't eat yet, right? Let's eat together—
- Well...

22
00:02:06,290 --> 00:02:09,420
there's a report that I need to receive. I'm hanging up.

23
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:41,190
Should we have a drink?

24
00:02:42,110 --> 00:02:46,580
I just hung up on Kwon Seok Woo.

25
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:49,070
I'll just drive you there.

26
00:02:49,070 --> 00:02:53,580
You're curious about why Shi Hyun's living outside of the home, too.

27
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:19,590
You're here now?

28
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:22,030
What's this? Were you waiting for me?

29
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:24,650
No, I just know the sound of your footsteps.

30
00:03:24,650 --> 00:03:27,760
Aw, are you a puppy?

31
00:03:28,730 --> 00:03:30,540
Was the drawing work hard?

32
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:34,270
You sounded like you were trudging along.

33
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:38,200
- I want to eat ramen.
- Huh?

34
00:03:44,530 --> 00:03:47,000
Hey, I'll need to buy this, too.

35
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:52,340
It's what my mom taught me. I can't cook.

36
00:03:56,850 --> 00:04:00,360
An egg with ramen is the best.

37
00:04:02,690 --> 00:04:06,640
I love it when someone cooks ramen for me.

38
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:09,360
I love eating ramen at your house.

39
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:13,300
You just like it because you're eating it with me.

40
00:04:17,330 --> 00:04:20,700
- What are you doing?
- Huh?
- In front of the fridge?

41
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,750
No, it's nothing.

42
00:04:29,170 --> 00:04:31,270
Why are you bringing rice from the fridge?

43
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:33,910
Ramen should have cold rice.

44
00:04:33,910 --> 00:04:35,020
Why?

45
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:39,200
Oh, you see, it's simple if you explain it in terms of osmotic pressure,

46
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:43,350
the amylose and amylopectin that makes up rice—

47
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:46,060
My head hurts.

48
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:47,990
Okay.

49
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:51,570
Okay, I'll remember this. Ramen and cold rice.

50
00:04:51,570 --> 00:04:55,360
One skill has been added to Kwon Shi Hyun's life skills.

51
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:58,080
Wow, it's really sparkling.

52
00:04:58,080 --> 00:05:00,200
- It's no joke.
- Right?

53
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:02,250
I can come often, right?

54
00:05:03,180 --> 00:05:05,680
What are you even saying?

55
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:13,780
You know how they call the time for the light of a star to reach here a light year?

56
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:16,150
Isn't that a bit sad?

57
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:21,280
But, if we're being exact,

58
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:24,460
a light year is the amount of distance light travels through space in a year,

59
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:29,720
the astronomical lines and the aeon parsecs travel between the celestial bodies—

60
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:33,730
You know right? That I become a beast when my head hurts.

61
00:05:35,380 --> 00:05:37,230
Okay, fine.

62
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:40,740
But, what are you sad about?

63
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:44,400
Just that... How I came to shine,

64
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:48,780
how I laughed, how I spoke,

65
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:54,780
someone will find out about all that a long time after it happened.

66
00:05:56,950 --> 00:06:00,380
You should show me right away and tell me right away.

67
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:04,600
Since I'll be close by, I'll know soon.

68
00:06:10,130 --> 00:06:15,290
Really? Shi Hyun really isn't his biological son?

69
00:06:17,590 --> 00:06:20,530
The vice chairman doesn't know that I know.

70
00:06:22,170 --> 00:06:24,420
Why did you tell me?

71
00:06:24,420 --> 00:06:27,320
It's information that you need to know.

72
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:30,120
This is all I can do for you, too.

73
00:06:32,580 --> 00:06:35,700
It would be interesting if the chairwoman knew.

74
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:40,080
I heard that the reason why the vice chairman seat was given to him so quickly was because of Shi Hyun.

75
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,050
No one else knows about it, right?

76
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:50,010
Tiuzen passing, the marriage, the name of the foundation, the Bio stocks...

77
00:06:50,010 --> 00:06:54,160
This has to be kept a secret until my claim's been secured.

78
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:58,390
And, we need to check if that's really the case for Shi Hyun.

79
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:05,660
Mi Ri, do you really have to get married?

80
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,960
What kind of question is that?

81
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:11,260
I just want you to find an easier person to be around.

82
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:14,250
Senior, comfort and a comfortable relationship...

83
00:07:14,250 --> 00:07:16,510
There's a relationship that offers more than that.

84
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:21,050
Am I easy to be around? Are you comfortable around me?

85
00:07:21,050 --> 00:07:23,060
It's probably no for both.

86
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:28,360
To me, you're a comfortable person to be around. But you're not someone who can give me comfort.

87
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:32,430
So, if you're trying to stop me, don't tell me about these things.

88
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:52,460
What's with your expression?

89
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:54,610
- Everything changed.
- What?

90
00:07:54,610 --> 00:07:58,030
It's not even the theater where we watched movies.

91
00:07:58,030 --> 00:08:00,260
It's not where we used to eat, either.

92
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:03,820
That's true.

93
00:08:03,820 --> 00:08:07,880
I was excited when I came, but now I'm sad.

94
00:08:08,610 --> 00:08:13,970
Let's walk all night until we find somewhere that looks like how it did in the past.

95
00:08:18,590 --> 00:08:20,990
There was a place like this in Seoul?

96
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:24,780
The people that my eldest sister-in-law send all drive around in cars.

97
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:27,990
So, I have to hide in places like this.

98
00:08:27,990 --> 00:08:29,300
It's pretty.

99
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:33,050
Just follow me around. I'll show you a lot of fun places.

100
00:08:33,050 --> 00:08:34,560
Hey.

101
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:50,290
I was almost tricked by you, where do you think you're selling medicine to?

102
00:08:50,290 --> 00:08:52,080
What medicine did I sell?

103
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:56,580
You're different from Shi Hyun. Even your eyes can act when you're seducing women.

104
00:08:56,580 --> 00:08:57,960
Is it hard to work at a restaurant?

105
00:08:57,960 --> 00:09:01,400
You can't go playing around, so you have nowhere to flirt around, huh?

106
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:04,270
Okay, I got it, so just breathe when you talk.

107
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:08,250
With all that speculation, how is she going to become a famous cellist?

108
00:09:08,250 --> 00:09:09,450
What is he mumbling on about?

109
00:09:09,450 --> 00:09:11,330
So, Soo Ji is a Cancer sign.

110
00:09:11,330 --> 00:09:14,180
And there's a Gemini constellation nearby.

111
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:16,780
So Se Joo's next to her, then.

112
00:09:16,780 --> 00:09:19,240
They're both winter constellations.

113
00:09:20,650 --> 00:09:25,060
They say Aries and Gemini also have similar lifestyle rhythms.

114
00:09:25,060 --> 00:09:28,060
You and Se Joo are similar.

115
00:09:28,060 --> 00:09:32,410
That's true. I wake up at noon, and Se Joo wakes up at one.

116
00:09:33,010 --> 00:09:37,840
Then, you woke up early that time because of me?

117
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,570
Me? When?

118
00:09:39,570 --> 00:09:44,860
In the beginning when you would wait for me at dawn in the library.

119
00:09:44,860 --> 00:09:49,160
When you went to see the elders, you'd wake up early on the weekends, too.

120
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:51,760
That's true, I did.

121
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:54,070
Did you really want to appear that good in front of me?

122
00:09:54,070 --> 00:09:57,040
Did you really want to seduce me that much?

123
00:09:57,040 --> 00:10:00,260
