187
00:14:45,110 --> 00:14:47,930
I'll just look. Like this.

188
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:52,010
I'm being serious.

189
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:54,910
Forget it.

190
00:14:59,420 --> 00:15:05,080
Even now, if you told me to cover and hide you, I could do it.

191
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:10,970
I keep forgetting you. So I have to keep coming to see you.

192
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:19,840
The smell of your cologne.

193
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:23,730
For some time, on the second floor of the department store,

194
00:15:23,730 --> 00:15:27,400
I'd walk around so much to try and find this cologne.

195
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:31,760
