When I first met my husband, I talked to him first.

198
00:15:44,950 --> 00:15:47,810
I asked, "What cologne do you use?"

199
00:15:47,810 --> 00:15:53,410
After divorcing him, I felt sorry towards him.

200
00:15:56,000 --> 00:16:03,350
I was late for my lecture, so I was running up the stairs. And your mother was coming down so we brushed by each other.

201
00:16:03,350 --> 00:16:09,440
We just brushed by each other, but your mother came back, grabbed me, and asked,

202
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:11,780
"What cologne do you use?"

203
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:14,180
So, I told her,

204
00:16:14,180 --> 00:16:18,150
"I'll tell you if you buy me a cup of tea."

205
00:16:22,340 --> 00:16:24,640
