207
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:32,170
Later on, when I had gotten older,

208
00:16:32,170 --> 00:16:36,620
I asked her what she liked so much about a person who wasn't even fun like me.

209
00:16:39,450 --> 00:16:43,920
She said she wanted to keep meeting me because of the smell of my cologne.

210
00:16:45,610 --> 00:16:50,290
