219
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:33,850
I didn't even know I had it.

220
00:17:33,850 --> 00:17:37,240
- My mom bought me the same one that my dad uses.
- I see.

221
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:40,810
Do you want three marshmallows?

222
00:17:40,810 --> 00:17:43,890
No, I don't really like marshmallows.

223
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:51,590
I don't know if I like this cologne.

224
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:55,730
I don't really like it, either, since it reminds me of my dad.

225
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:09,980
I just like what you usually smell like.

226
00:18:10,950 --> 00:18:13,290
So cheesy!

227
00:18:13,290 --> 00:18:17,590
If Kyung Joo knows I'm like this, she might want to end our friendship.

