00:18:27,320 --> 00:18:28,950
Hey, I have to drink this first.

230
00:18:28,950 --> 00:18:31,620
No, you can take that and drink it. Go on.

231
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:35,130
You're going to sleep until noon, anyway. I'll be going.

